description:
This is a 32 minute workout called '30MIN full body hourglass pilates workout // slim and tone your body // beginner friendly' from the channel Lidia Mera.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
